---
title: Kale & Farro Bowls with a Fried Egg with Tomatoes, Guacamole, Feta & Scallion Chimichurri
description: This hearty and satisfying bowl will surely put some pep into your morning (or noon, no judgment!) saunter to the kitchen. Nutty farro and nutrient-rich kale make a delicious base for topping with charred tomatoes, fried eggs, creamy guacamole, tangy-salty feta cheese, and a punchy scallion chimichurri sauce. Serve with lemon wedges for a sunny spritz and a great way to start the day.
